column5: Fishing for 2.5 hrs but all fish caught in 1.5 hrs, gotta love this weather, TUBES TUBES & More TUBES, Dad had a blast, so did I Richard
hmmm... sounds like you are telling me to get my canoe back up there asap

Waters 45 degrees, better make sure you don't tip if you do, maybe we can get out again, let me know your schedule, I'm watching the weather & a few buddies are still trying to get out, little farther to go than last time maybe Richard
Good job. Good to see you and your Dad out for a sucessful afternoon on the water.
Can't beat time out on the water with the oldman, definitely my favorite kind of fishing...
Nice report! And good on ya for getting out with Dad. Man, what did people do before tubes? Jim
Great report and pics Richard Sounds like fun and your dad's smile says it all Thanks for sharing Leechman
Even without the fish... a great outing! Envy the company you keep...
